# Runtime output folders never belong in the station source mirror.
**/OUTPUT/**
**/REVIEW/**
**/ARCHIVE/**
**/ERROR/**
**/LOGS/**
**/logs/**
**/exports/**

# Databases, vector indexes, and model/ML artifacts.
**/*.db
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite3
**/*.db-wal
**/*.db-shm
**/*.faiss
**/*.hnsw
**/*.qdrant
**/*.chroma
**/*.pickle
**/*.pkl
**/*.pt
**/*.pth
**/*.bin
**/*.onnx
**/*.safetensors

# Secrets and local machine/runtime config.
**/.env
**/*.env
**/secrets.*
**/*secret*
**/*token*
**/CONFIG/*.json
**/CONFIG/*.ini
!**/CONFIG/*.example.json
!**/CONFIG/*.example.ini

# Generated logs/exports.
**/*.log
**/*.jsonl
**/*.parquet
**/*.arrow
